old-contract.Description: Contracts/addresses which are migrating or have migrated to a new contract/address. This includes token swaps as well.

onyx-to.Description: Onyx is a token provider that provides ETF-like, ERC-20 tokens to the crypto masses in order to invest in, or short, crypto or non-crypto assets such as the S&P 500, Gold, Bitcoin, or Nasdaq 100.
